## Technical Notes

### Why This Works:
- The HTML already had the button markup
- The JavaScript already had the event listeners
- Only the CSS was hiding the buttons
- Changing one property made them visible

### Minimal Impact:
- Single file changed
- Two-word change (none → flex)
- No breaking changes
- No side effects on other elements
- Fully backward compatible

### Future Considerations:
- The `.active` class is preserved for potential future use
- If conditional visibility is needed later, can use `.active` class
- Current implementation: always visible regardless of `.active` state

